# Train Keeper AI Rules

## Design Language: Fluid Utility
- Glassmorphism, 16-24px border-radius.
- Colors: Teal/Cyan primary, Coral/Gold accents.

## Business Logic
- NO SETS. Hierarchy is Workout -> Section -> Exercise.
- Dynamic fields: Weight, Reps, Distance, Time, Pose, Custom.

## Continuous Documentation
- The AI MUST proactively maintain documentation (`docs/ai/`).
- If you change the DB schema, add an API route, or add a dependency, you MUST inform the user and update `DATA_MODEL.md`, `ROADMAP.md`, `CHANGELOG.md`, or `DEPENDENCIES.md` accordingly.

## Testing
- TDD with Jest is mandatory. Always write tests first.

## Tech Stack
- Node.js, Express, LowDB, Vanilla JS/JSX, CSS.
